{"tid":2409170,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"出嚟做嘢越嚟越少朋友","createTime":"2021-02-15T14:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T16:54:45.000Z","uid":31818,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"83b24071462e90763a925fe68f0fa0702ba0dc33","tid":2409170,"uid":31818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T14:42:37.000Z","msg":"（sor我歸納咗友情都係感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n本身讀大學嗰陣就識到一班hibye friend，<br />\n出嚟玩出嚟食就約，平時就無嘢講嗰啲ocamp mate<br />\n中學都有一兩個朋友，<br />\n但佢地出咗社會就好似唔同曬，<br />\n又港女又拜金又出軌總之同我自己嘅價值觀好唔夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由本身有三四個真心friend到依家得返一個，<br />\n成個生活都好似得返拍拖，做嘢，打機，自己興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時見到人地instagram post相好開心出去都覺得有啲心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時覺得唔啱key嘅就唔好做朋友，<br />\n但又真係越嚟越少朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3940320bf13a6f5c3fa41d003a7784deaa0b84","tid":2409170,"uid":305631,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T14:58:59.000Z","msg":"冇咪冇囉"},{"pid":"37cea8491da36d6b560c8c3724ad549d408b4c78","tid":2409170,"uid":218575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:00:18.000Z","msg":"本來就無朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018922870f34197929bb94a452379fb0d3fe7341","tid":2409170,"uid":118490,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:01:41.000Z","msg":"跟住好朋友仲要結咪婚唔得閒理你<br />\n最後無晒朋友"},{"pid":"61144f42a7cfab77ce5da786cd7213bb7092a704","tid":2409170,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:06:07.000Z","msg":"毒撚係咁"},{"pid":"2a30f6d0f2dc31c6a5c28f43e606aeacd9a1391b","tid":2409170,"uid":131259,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:07:11.000Z","msg":"有得拍拖其實已經唔差"},{"pid":"5840f373959636fac00f9700080bd9a9441c30eb","tid":2409170,"uid":182529,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:07:33.000Z","msg":"有拖拍仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d28d565c5567fe2fac9495e0844f81bef15bde","tid":2409170,"uid":177132,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:08:56.000Z","msg":"無拖拍又無朋友點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b139692a38642614fb4494c0cc7ffa4bb5d9ddd","tid":2409170,"uid":31818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"61144f42a7cfab77ce5da786cd7213bb7092a704","tid":2409170,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:06:07.000Z","msg":"毒撚係咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:11:20.000Z","msg":"我都真係毒撚，起碼唔鍾意做social queen，又唔鍾意多人"},{"pid":"7c072ed9de561f94e9e98dd9789df317c5977dcc","tid":2409170,"uid":31818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a30f6d0f2dc31c6a5c28f43e606aeacd9a1391b","tid":2409170,"uid":131259,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:07:11.000Z","msg":"有得拍拖其實已經唔差"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:13:59.000Z","msg":"我明呀，但就好似其他時間都自己一個咁"},{"pid":"db5e29c2f75df0a9db761032f500f779a6278bd2","tid":2409170,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b139692a38642614fb4494c0cc7ffa4bb5d9ddd","tid":2409170,"uid":31818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"61144f42a7cfab77ce5da786cd7213bb7092a704","tid":2409170,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02